text: Nurse Jackie is an American comedy-drama television series. It began on June 8, 2009. It is on Showtime, Movie Central and The Movie Network. It stars Edie Falco as an emergency room nurse at a hospital in New York City. ==Main characters== Actor Role Season Edie Falco Jackie Peyton, RN Eve Best Eleanor O'Hara MD Merritt Wever Zoey Barkow Paul Schulze Eddie Walzer R.Ph.
